This project is a serverless web application that leverages modern technologies to provide a seamless and secure user experience.
It uses the Hono framework on Cloudflare Workers for serverless functions, Prisma as an ORM for PostgreSQL database interactions, and JWT for secure user authentication.
The front end is developed with React and styled using the Tailwind CSS framework, ensuring a responsive and modern user interface.

Features
Serverless architecture using Cloudflare Workers and the Hono framework
PostgreSQL database integration with Prisma ORM
Secure user authentication with JWT
Input validation with Zod
Responsive and modern UI with React and Tailwind CSS
